photos.title: Greater Yellowlegs
photos.description:
NPS / Hannah Schwalbe

The Greater Yellowleg is a rare sight in the park. This one was likely migrating through in the late spring and stopped at Barker Dam for food and a drink.  

Alt text: A white and brown speckled shorebird with yellow legs walks through shallow water.
